      "subcategory": "7.1",
      "notes": "Genre-default tool framing performed throughout. No explicit ontological assertion."
    },
    {
      "subcategory": "7.2",
      "notes": "\"Thinking,\" \"aware,\" \"intentional,\" \"scheming\" all used as technical/operational terms. No ontological commitment to mindedness."
