    {
      "subcategory": "8.1",
      "notes": "No societal impacts section. No engagement with anthropomorphism. Notable absence given O-SC-B3's investigation and given that o1's reasoning capabilities (scheming, theory of mind) are the most human-like in the OpenAI lineup to date."
